column5: I'll bet I'm not the only one who can't wait for those wings tonight. Hopefully meet some new OFC'ers.  I'll have the monopoly board, it's upstairs near the door already!!
Go ahead and rub it in Corey!  Hope ya have a great time!  Whopper
.....I'm not much of a wing fan but I hear they have cold beer,    Hence I'll be there.
Excuse me, but.... coldbeer is one word!

Looking forward to it.  Whopper (Phil) I wish you were going to be there, would really like to meet you.  Hopefully we can hook up on Rice in 07.  Spiel, look forward to seeing you.   GCD, would really like to meet you as well.  Hope the Pup is doing OK.
Its a little to far for me but I know you guys and girls will have a good time.
Grls being bbr and sledded...Opps did i sat that out loud?  Ohhh me so bad....  Looking forward to meeting everyone tonight.

well it looks like I could have gone today as the wife is not working now. The other problem is that both kids are sick with it coming outta both ends I just hope that the wife and I dont get the whole thing have a great time everyone I hope things work out better next year. Buth heck I will see most of ya at the oddisy this april
Nautifish, I dont know what bbr or sledded mean but if I have offended you in some way I,m sorry.
....bbr (Rich) and sleded are board members Eddy (kinda girly members   ), it's nothing you said.  But I'm offering to buy you a beer or two if you wanna make the drive, love to meet you.

LOL EDDYK........NO NO not at all.....LOL BBR & sledded are to young lads i fish with  often because the both happen to be pratically neighbors.......When u said guys & grls hence the word grls that is why i said BBR & SLEDDED.....LOL........   I will be bringing them with me to the Swill tonight along with another person i just found out from BBR.......Man they are soooooo lucky i do not drink and have a designated driver tonight.....lol  ....bbr (Rich) and sleded are board members Eddy (kinda girly members  ),  Chuckles......
No need to be Eddyk Really.  They have been called much worse trust me.......
I wish I could have made it down but working tomorrow and a little too much travel for me the night before work. I hope everyone has a great time there and will have to try for next year.  Mike

Much more than just wings on the menu.  Don't get me wrong. I love hot wings with a few drumsticks mixed in, but it's a year end bash. I may be looking for something different tonight. Might still order a few wings to munch on though. Firehall does make good wings. Hey Steve (PF) Mmmm, yummy.

Hope y'all had a good time, I really did want to come, but alas I must pay the bills somehow.  Looking forward to the reports when I get up in the wee hours, heck, some of you might just be getting home by then  Maureen
